ygData.messageBody:
Hail Seekers of Knowledge, I am a Barbarian Warrior Princess of the 12th
Rank. Lately I have been spending my time in and around the Dwarves and
Elves on their island, and have killed a whole bunch of Orcs from the Clan
Crushbone. Currently I am in East Commons and plan to make the run to
Rivendale or Qeynos tonight. If you see me just call me Patty.

For the Honor and Glory of Rallos Zek;

Patty of Halas
